posts.description: Extreme Knitting without needles - yes we can. Join me for a two hour workshop where you make one of four projects. Swipe through images above. Hosted by the KPC Yarn Sydney Pop-Up on Sunday 21st of May and Saturday 27th of May. We will be using special 1kg bumps of #K1S1 in a limited range of colours. Choose your colour on the day.  Where: 14 William Street, Paddington, Sydney, Australia.  Bookings: through www.kpcyarn.bigcartel.com/products.  Class costs $195 including materials and light refreshments. Space is limited. If you can't make those times email me as we have the option of adding a night class as well. Can't wait to play. ''Tis always fun and therapeutic xx
